{%- comment -%}
============================================================================
HTML-PRODUCT-SCHEMA-DEBUG
============================================================================
Debug snippet — toont Shopify's native `{{ product | structured_data }}`
filter output als extra JSON-LD block op de product pagina.

DOEL:
Vergelijken wat Shopify native produceert vs. de Doran Product Reviews app
output (die al aanwezig is in de server-HTML).

ACTIVATIE — alleen zichtbaar wanneer één van deze waar is:
  - ?schemadebug=1 (of welke waarde dan ook) in de URL
  - admin theme editor preview (request.design_mode)

Normale bezoekers en Google-crawlers zien dit block NIET, dus geen
schema-conflict in production.

VERGELIJKEN:
  1. Open een PDP met ?schemadebug=1
  2. DevTools → Elements → zoek "application/ld+json"
  3. Er zouden nu 3 blocks moeten zijn:
       - Organization (html-theme-schema)
       - Product (Doran app-embed, reeds aanwezig)
       - Product met data-source="shopify-native-debug" (dit snippet)

TIJDELIJK — verwijder dit snippet (en de render call in
sections/block-product-information.liquid) zodra de vergelijking klaar is.

USAGE:
  {% render 'html-product-schema-debug', product: product %}
============================================================================
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- comment -%}
  TIJDELIJK: altijd aan voor korte vergelijking met Doran's output.
  VERWIJDER dit snippet en de render call in block-product-information.liquid
  zodra de vergelijking is gedaan — anders conflicteert dit met Doran.
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- if product != blank -%}
<script type="application/ld+json" data-source="shopify-native-debug">
{{ product | structured_data }}
</script>

{%- comment -%}
  ----------------------------------------------------------------------
  DIAGNOSTIC MODE — altijd output, plus HTML-comment met ruwe dump van
  product.metafields.shopify.* zodat we kunnen zien welke keys aanwezig
  zijn, welke types, en welke waardes.

  Zodra we weten wat er in zit, maken we dit productie-waardig.
  ----------------------------------------------------------------------
{%- endcomment -%}

<!-- SCHEMA-DEBUG-MARKER: snippet v4 (metaobject-dereference) -->
<!-- SCHEMA-DEBUG: iteration dump met metaobject field-probes
{%- for pair in product.metafields.shopify -%}
  iter_key={{ pair[0] }} | type={{ pair[1].type }}
  {%- if pair[1].type contains 'list.' -%}
    {%- for item in pair[1].value -%}
      | item.label={{ item.label }} | item.name={{ item.name }} | item.display_name={{ item.display_name }} | item.system.handle={{ item.system.handle }} | item.handle={{ item.handle }}
    {%- endfor -%}
  {%- else -%}
    | val.label={{ pair[1].value.label }} | val.name={{ pair[1].value.name }} | val.display_name={{ pair[1].value.display_name }}
  {%- endif -%}
{% endfor -%}
END iteration dump -->

{%- capture properties_json -%}
  {%- assign first = true -%}
  {%- for pair in product.metafields.shopify -%}
    {%- assign mf_key = pair[0] -%}
    {%- assign mf = pair[1] -%}
    {%- if mf == blank or mf.value == blank -%}{%- continue -%}{%- endif -%}

    {%- assign label = mf_key | replace: '_', ' ' | replace: '-', ' ' | capitalize -%}

    {%- if mf.type contains 'list.' -%}
      {%- for item in mf.value -%}
        {%- comment -%} Metaobject-referenties hebben meestal .label, anders .name / .display_name, anders handle {%- endcomment -%}
        {%- if item.label != blank -%}
          {%- assign item_str = item.label -%}
        {%- elsif item.name != blank -%}
          {%- assign item_str = item.name -%}
        {%- elsif item.display_name != blank -%}
          {%- assign item_str = item.display_name -%}
        {%- elsif item.handle != blank -%}
          {%- assign item_str = item.handle -%}
        {%- else -%}
          {%- capture item_str -%}{{ item }}{%- endcapture -%}
          {%- assign item_str = item_str | strip -%}
        {%- endif -%}
        {%- if item_str == blank -%}{%- continue -%}{%- endif -%}
        {%- unless first -%},{%- endunless -%}{%- assign first = false -%}
        {"@type":"PropertyValue","name":{{ label | json }},"value":{{ item_str | json }}}
      {%- endfor -%}
    {%- else -%}
      {%- if mf.value.label != blank -%}
        {%- assign val_str = mf.value.label -%}
      {%- elsif mf.value.name != blank -%}
        {%- assign val_str = mf.value.name -%}
      {%- elsif mf.value.display_name != blank -%}
        {%- assign val_str = mf.value.display_name -%}
      {%- else -%}
        {%- capture val_str -%}{{ mf.value }}{%- endcapture -%}
        {%- assign val_str = val_str | strip -%}
      {%- endif -%}
      {%- if val_str == blank -%}{%- continue -%}{%- endif -%}
      {%- unless first -%},{%- endunless -%}{%- assign first = false -%}
      {"@type":"PropertyValue","name":{{ label | json }},"value":{{ val_str | json }}}
    {%- endif -%}
  {%- endfor -%}
{%- endcapture -%}

{%- assign properties_json = properties_json | strip -%}

<script type="application/ld+json" data-source="shopify-native-debug-additional">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org/",
  "@id": {{ product.url | append: '#product' | json }},
  "@type": "Product",
  "additionalProperty": [{{ properties_json }}]
}
</script>

{%- endif -%}
